    "description": "If you're a passionate Surgeon with drive and ambition, Medanta Consulting Pvt Ltd in Surat is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Medanta Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMedanta Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Medanta Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
